
    - Loading Target Webpages to Source Webpage without refreshing the whole webpage called as Single Page Application.44

    - Loading the Target Webpages to the Source Webpage called as Routing.

    - In AngularJS We Can Achieve the Routing in 2 ways.

        1.ngRoute Module

        2.ui.router Module.


Steps to Design the Single Page Application By using ngRoute Module.

1.download the ngRoute Module.

2.Add the ngRoute Module Depenedency.

3.Create the Target Templates.

4.Create the Controllers.

5.Done the Mapping.
